_sText:
Map name: aim_cmd_street
Made by_ kaos4u
Date: 04/08/07
Filesize: 1.61 MB
Player Spawn Points: 40+
Contact info: kaos4u2004@yahoo.com or solidsurf.info

================================

This map was inspired by the layout from aim_furious made by: Axzer.  I fallowed the same lay-out guidelines but added more realistic detail that resembles a bombed out set of houses.  I didn't want to add to much detail that it would strey away from the gameplay of the original map design.  

Note: The red wooden house has some invisible bullet proof textures guarding the player from bullets shot through the walls.  Also every player will spawn with a deagle instead of USP/Glock.  Buyzones are still included at spawn.

Special thanks to: |CMD| clan for hosting and inspiring this map.  Also, thanks to Axzer for inspiring a fun proven layout.  My only hopes is this map is as fun as aim_furious.
